{"tid":397683,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲明知佢唔會係最後一個都會繼續一齊？","createTime":"2017-09-12T16:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T01:56:50.000Z","uid":43289,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2832ad7ebad8ad133cb80c2e6a1e78aa5ac49b81","tid":397683,"uid":43289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"咩條路自己揀仆街唔好喊<br />\n我聽左十鳩幾次<br />\n但係我完全唔覺得佢嘅將來會有我<br />\n佢對將來係零計劃<br />\n有時諗起佢真係心都灰埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知點解自己仲咁蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲對佢咁好<br />\n明知佢唔會珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係唔知點繼續行落去"},{"pid":"29fefc53e9bbb4fde66c67bb4bf0617a12202b20","tid":397683,"uid":73152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"點解會覺得行唔到落去？"},{"pid":"a5f6cd213848c61d39af50da8cede3556c4e81f2","tid":397683,"uid":40847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T16:40:04.000Z","msg":"點樣明知 你係未來人？"},{"pid":"588015d934eb34b68c26b20e038ecbd727f7aff1","tid":397683,"uid":14042,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n明知佢唔岩我<br />\n佢仲同我一齊 只係未搵到個更好<br />\n有時我唔開心同佢講 <br />\n佢理都唔想理<br />\n<br />\n但我真係唔捨得講分手<br />\n我仲要longd 緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bce9c2277637941e5730c775e258577414388c4","tid":397683,"uid":43289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T17:43:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係<br />\n明知佢唔岩我<br />\n佢仲同我一齊 只係未搵到個更好<br />\n有時我唔開心同佢講 <br />\n佢理都唔想理<br />\n<br />\n但我真係唔捨得講分手<br />\n我仲要longd 緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n純粹好奇<br />\n邊到同邊到嘅long d?"},{"pid":"b609422d29fb9fc10ed47cd9865326a1aad9d099","tid":397683,"uid":43289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T17:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blo